  '  <li><strong>Hash / token / signature compares without <code>timingSafeEqual</code></strong> — every <code>===</code> against a variable named <code>hash</code> / <code>token</code> / <code>sig</code> / <code>mac</code> / <code>digest</code> flags.</li>',
